Oh yes, well - my other brothers too I mean look I wouldn't go washing for my brother at Astley Bridge every week if I didn't think something of him would I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 You got on well as children though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Who did you play with, did you play with your brothers and sisters or neighbours?
