\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Yes, we - we - well round about us when - when I was young there were quite a lot of children, 
you know, we never sort of had to go far from home to have a friend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Where did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 On the street, yes, on the street. There's no room to play in the house when there were eight of us in you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Well - we - we didn't - make a - a mess of ourselves but we never - we never came home like we went out you know, sort of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Was there anyone that your parents used to stop you playing with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Well I can't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 You were allowed to play with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Oh yes, we'd play -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 No, we didn't have them then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Do you remember the games you played as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6244688\charrsid12015374 Oh well I used to play - I was always playing house with
 a doll, I had a lovely doll which was all kid - kid dolly and pot - pot from here, pot hands and pot from knee down you know and little toes, pot feet it had and - and two boys used to live next door but one to me and we used to go and play - outside chu
rch - and some girls wanted me to - to go and do something I forget now what it was that they were doing, I went to play with 'em and so as these two boys were going home and I said to them would they take my dolly home, you know. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 And they did and on the wa
y - on their way home, they - I don't know if they smashed its face or if - it had a beautiful pot face, I don't know if they smashed its face or if they left it fall but its only - I don't think its twelve months since I got rid of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Did you play any other games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 
Oh - oh we - we used to build houses on the - get a lot of stones and build a house and - and sort of play mothers and fathers, you know, and - I - perhaps a younger child would be a - oh yes, we used to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Did you have any hobbies or did you collect anything or do gardening, you had a cat?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Yes, at home, yes, we had a cat but - you don't see many cats these days although the lady that used to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 You didn't keep cats as a child, you just had one cat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Oh - we just had one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Did you have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 
We used to go - we - oh yes, used to have a bicycle, yes, we had a bicycle. I used to go to the glass making class up at the Methodist school. But funnily enough I - and I used to make lots of things but I
 never like things I make myself. Funny that, I don't know why.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 When you went bicycling who did you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Well I went - I went with - me sister that's - here. 'Cos she got a bicycle. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6244688\charrsid12015374 She saved up - well she had some money in the no-op and we 
used to save up in the Coop, they had a small savings club at the Co-op and you used to take it every Friday night and she kept saving up, this were money that our parents had five of us you know and we - we saved up and we used to take it up to the Co-op
 and - one day she decided she wanted a bicycle, she'd like a bicycle. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 
So she went and drew some money out of the co-op for this bicycle and this brother where I go to said to her, here, silly, he says, you'll never put it back again. You'll never get the money back in the Co-op again. And she never did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Did you take part in any sports apart from that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 No, I can't - oh, played tennis, used to play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Did you go to theatres or concerts or music halls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Or cinemas, while you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Well - no. Things didn't always fit in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 But you never went as a child while you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Oh no. No, I don't think - we ever - they ever took any of them to the pictures at the - from the school. They do now you know but -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 How old were you when you first went to school?
