No, you see, that - that was - that's the sort of - well, punctual, we used to have to be - you - we couldn't go walking in like they do today, I mean, that lady was on the - done that, because we, I never see - I nev
er see it these days, I don't know if they do it but we'd all to - to line up in a line, the whistle used to blow and we'd all to line up in a line in the - in the - row after row according to the classes you see, and - we used to walk in the school like 
that. I don't know if they do it now, I never see them do it up at our school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 
