\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Well there again you see I mean I can't ever remember having to be punished for anything. It's not me -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Do you remember anyone else being punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 No, I don't really. I don't honestly. No. I mean, it looks as though I - like we were goody-goodies but I don't remember
 anything - anybody being punished you know. I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Do you remember anything they did say was important in life, that they taught you was important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Well - I - I don't think, No, I - I can't say that they - you know, when - when I went
 to school we used to have copy books where you used to have to do - that's why I think I get the good writing you know - but they don't have copy books now do they. I - I have a nephew who's really clever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 They were very keen on writing at your school were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11339190 NT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 
Well - no I think it was due the - well - probably they - probably that was it, they; used to use these copy books with - was the - the - c's and the d's and everything and you had to make them like it you see. Whether that was what made
 us good writers or not I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Were your parents ever interested in your schoolwork and did they ever visit the school or see the teachers?
