\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4467992 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid135013\charrsid12015374 Do you think you benefitted by your education?
